Various Otyebis Crew:




The transmission was received by the gi-normous craft and a reply 
transmission was sent to Tankor.

"Thank you, Tankor, Strika, Thrust, Obsidian, and Jetstorm for entering the 
IGL's Regular Division. We have you all registered and thank you for your 
promptness.  We need one last piece of information for this to be final.  Are 
you part of a faction, and if the answer is yes what is the name of the 
faction?  Thanks again."
